Date: 10/10/2002
Source: Taranaki Daily News
Author:
Vol / Page: 21
Edition:
Quote: What are they going to do with the developing Peak Notes fiasco? Peak Notes were designed as a capital funding mechanism for the cost of stainless steel required to process farmers' milk. If you supply more milk at the height [peak] of the production season you force the company to install more and bigger plant and you therefore help pay for that extra requirement by buying more Peak Notes .. farmers are struggling with all of the rules that impact on Peak Notes and there is a fundamental inequity in the system.
